sentences.english: They booked us into a tuppeny-ha'penny hotel near the docks.
sentences.chinese: 他们为我们在离码头不远处订了个廉价旅馆。

sentences.english: This paper analyses several factors which influences the self - priming pump of the unloader of Ore Terminal .
sentences.chinese: 分析了影响矿石码头卸船机自吸泵的几个因素。

sentences.english: We took the children to the dock to see the ships.
sentences.chinese: 我们带孩子们到码头去看轮船。

sentences.english: The ship lies alongside the wharf.; The steamer lies at the pier.
In order to get next to a dock, a vessel had to turn its rudder to the outside.
sentences.chinese: 为了靠上码头，船只必须将船舵转向外侧。

sentences.english: Alert Bay is also the first marina we have stopped at that is truly affordable on our budget.
sentences.chinese: 阿乐湾也是我们停留的码头中最符合我们预算的。

sentences.english: The port near our city will be opened to foreign ships.
sentences.chinese: 我们城市附近的码头将为外国轮船开放。

sentences.english: Also provided a powerful safeguard for the gravity quay construction of large caisson.
sentences.chinese: 也为大型沉箱结构重力式码头建设提供了有力的保障。

sentences.english: Can you guarantee the stevedores not to steal the goods?
sentences.chinese: 你能保证码头工人不偷货吗？

sentences.english: From the dock here you can rent watercraft and do something that very few know about it.
sentences.chinese: 你可以在这里的码头上租船并且做一些你不了解的事。

sentences.english: The demolishment of the Star Ferry Pier in 2006 intensified such movements.
sentences.chinese: 2006年，天星码头的迁拆更强化了这类行动。

sentences.english: I'm only fit for a roustabout.
We would have some water in our loading dock in the back.
sentences.chinese: 我们本来在我们的码头装货水在后面。

sentences.english: Love rivers have wound the life, only then sees sweetheart's fisherman wharf.
sentences.chinese: 爱情河流过蜿蜒了生活，才看见情人的渔人码头。

sentences.english: A fishing trawler unloads crates of frozen fish.
sentences.chinese: 渔船在码头卸下的一箱箱冷冻海鱼。
